claim.claim-text:
The radio resource range setting method according to any of Claims 13 to 15, further comprises, 

acquiring priority band information representing a priority band that is a communication band used preferentially for radio communication in a communication area adjacent to a communication area allocated to the base station; 

for the plurality of communication terminals, acquiring communication path quality information representing a communication path quality that is a quality of a communication path between the edge communication terminal and the base station.
